{"tid":2268550,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人隻貓有口炎？","createTime":"2020-11-03T01:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:03:25.000Z","uid":208973,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6c76db2fc2a5eab6cbeeff9393ec75ecef513e","tid":2268550,"uid":208973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"我隻貓差唔多一歲大<br />\n近呢兩個月牙肉紅得好勁 口又好臭<br />\n買左枝野搽 但搽唔好<br />\n所以就帶左佢睇醫生<br />\n發現原來係貓口炎黎 係一個貓好common既病黎<br />\n但醫生話其實都冇咩藥可以根治到貓口炎<br />\n建議我地做一個全口拔牙既手術<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉 過幾星期就做手術<br />\n雖然好心痛佢一歲就要冇哂啲牙<br />\n但我諗咁樣係對佢最c服<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人可以分享下"},{"pid":"082a3c23bd3c4e0af1ee481e75a69dbc1d5481be","tid":2268550,"uid":43594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"1歲就口炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以講下獸醫話咩成因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食濕糧唔刷牙？"},{"pid":"c8cf18643fed777d7c47e5027982304c68de6185","tid":2268550,"uid":156997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:21:12.000Z","msg":"口炎嚴重嘅話會斷牙根同個口成日流血，<br />\n加埋啲菌有機會入血，<br />\n快啲帶貓貓去睇！！！<br />\n<br />\nPs: 我隻已經剝哂牙。"},{"pid":"afd5dcadd723d9f2e2505f1f64eac354e8cd1e3a","tid":2268550,"uid":156997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"想佢繼續開心、食到肥肥白白反而剝牙會幫到佢，<br />\n雖然一開始係要時間復原，<br />\n但之後你會見到貓貓其實會食多咗嘢，<br />\n比以前開心好多"},{"pid":"17951423d7a5deb76cb8eacb1bfeee5b99b39cf5","tid":2268550,"uid":208973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"082a3c23bd3c4e0af1ee481e75a69dbc1d5481be","tid":2268550,"uid":43594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"1歲就口炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以講下獸醫話咩成因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />